00:19:11,250 --> 00:19:12,080
That's why...

256
00:19:12,080 --> 00:19:14,500
you want to find out for yourself.

257
00:19:16,010 --> 00:19:17,160
Do it.

258
00:19:18,380 --> 00:19:22,640
Meet with Amber and talk to her.

259
00:19:24,140 --> 00:19:25,320
Huang!

260
00:19:25,320 --> 00:19:26,470
Hop in.

261
