268
00:19:53,170 --> 00:19:55,390
Evacuate as soon as you can, Misaki!

269
00:19:55,390 --> 00:19:56,500
Evacuate?

270
00:19:56,500 --> 00:19:58,220
I'll explain the details later.

271
00:19:58,220 --> 00:19:59,990
Leave Tokyo at once!

272
00:20:00,430 --> 00:20:03,050
What's going on? Don't tell me...

273
00:20:09,740 --> 00:20:14,020
whatever happened in South  America is about to take place here...

274
00:20:18,570 --> 00:20:20,820
At the moment, we have two primary objectives:

275
00:20:21,310 --> 00:20:24,110
Lead the dolls into the gate,

276
00:20:24,110 --> 00:20:26,410
and destroy the particle accelerator.

277
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:39,210
Let's go.

278
00:20:41,150 --> 00:20:45,020
